    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! I\u2019m finally parting with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty has been my reliable companion for years, and honestly, she still drives like a dream. I\u2019ve always made sure she got the TLC she deserved, from regular check-ups to keeping the interior nice and cozy. There are a couple of tiny beauty marks here and there\u2014just little signs of the great adventures we\u2019ve had together\u2014but nothing that takes away from her classic charm or smooth performance. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable, spirited ride that\u2019s ready for its next chapter, come on by and let\u2019s chat. You\u2019re going to love how she handles the road!",
      "price": 34500.0,
